      Appl : ∀ {τ₁ τ₂}{r₁ r₂}{e₁ : Expression ev tv r₁}{e₂ : Expression ev tv r₂} 
           → Q , Qg , Γ ⊢ e₁ ∶ funType τ₁ τ₂ 
